---
title: Bocconcini Salad with Rigatoni, Almonds and Basil Pesto
description: Tonight's pasta salad is packed with cherry tomatoes, broiled zucchini, fragrant basil pesto and creamy bocconcini. These fresh and herbaceous flavours are perfect to brighten up a wintery day!
